  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Digital Marketing Strategist",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a Digital Marketing Strategist to support the company’s digital marketing initiatives and brand presence for our central kitchen and food production solutions.</p><p>The role focuses on planning and executing digital marketing activities, improving online visibility, and supporting business\ngrowth through digital channels.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><p>·      Plan and execute digital marketing campaigns across online platforms</p><p>·      Manage and optimise company website, social media and digital content</p><p>·      Support brand positioning and online communication for central kitchen and food-related solutions</p><p>·      Assist in developing marketing strategies to reach B2B customers, partners and distributors</p><p>·      Monitor digital campaign performance and prepare basic reports and insights</p><p>·      Coordinate marketing materials to ensure consistency with brand guidelines</p><p>·      Support lead generation and online customer engagement activities</p><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p>·      Bachelor’s degree or above in Marketing, Digital Marketing, Communications, Business or related fields</p><p>·      Strong understanding of digital marketing fundamentals</p><p>·      Familiarity with social media platforms, content management and online marketing tools</p><p>·      Ability to analyse basic digital performance metrics</p><p>·      Good communication and organisational skills</p><p>·      Ability to work independently and manage multiple tasks</p><h3><strong>Preferred / Advantageous</strong></h3><p>·      Experience or exposure to B2B marketing, F&B or food-related industries</p><p>·      Knowledge of digital marketing trends and content planning</p><p>·      Ability to support structured content and online engagement</p><p>·      Exposure to regional or overseas markets is an advantage</p>",
